
    <title>Additional Health Resources</title>
    

    <%- include('../partials/header') %>

    <main class="container my-5">
        <h1 class="text-center mb-4">Additional Health Resources</h1>
        <p class="lead text-center">Take advantage of these valuable resources that will support you on your journey to better health. From apps to videos, we've got you covered.</p>

        <section>
            <h2>Health Apps</h2>
            <ul>
                <li><strong><a href="https://www.myfitnesspal.com/">MyFitnessPal</a></strong>: A calorie tracking app to help you manage your diet and track your fitness goals.</li>
                <li><strong><a href="https://www.headspace.com/">Headspace</a></strong>: A meditation app for mindfulness and stress reduction.</li>
                <li><strong><a href="https://www.strava.com/">Strava</a></strong>: A fitness tracker for runners and cyclists to log workouts and challenge friends.</li>
            </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>Community Support</h2>
            <ul>
                <li><strong><a href="https://www.mentalhealth.gov/get-help/online-mental-health-services">Online Support Groups</a></strong>: Find virtual support groups for various health conditions like diabetes, mental health, and weight loss.</li>
                <li><strong><a href="https://www.verywellfit.com/find-a-support-group-4176340">Local Health Programs</a></strong>: Check for local wellness programs and support organizations in your area.</li>
            </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>Videos</h2>
            <ul>
                <li><strong><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dNnR_Nk2OpY">Yoga for Beginners</a></strong>: A beginner-friendly yoga routine to get you started on your wellness journey.</li>
                <li><strong><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=EZkgc-fv2gI">Healthy Cooking</a></strong>: Videos on how to cook nutritious and delicious meals.</li>
                <li><strong><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FZavt08D7hw">Mental Health Talks</a></strong>: Educational videos from mental health professionals discussing stress, anxiety, and coping strategies.</li>
            </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>Telemedicine Services</h2>
            <ul>
                <li><strong><a href="https://www.teladoc.com/">Book a Virtual Doctor Appointment</a></strong>: Links to platforms where you can schedule consultations with doctors online.</li>
                <li><strong><a href="https://www.betterhelp.com/">Mental Health Counseling</a></strong>: Online therapy platforms where you can speak with licensed therapists remotely.</li>
            </ul>
        </section>
    </main>

